title: What Digital Camera. December 2010.
description:
What Digital Camera. December 2010.

What Digital Camera - the UK's best digital photography magazine 
provides the most in-depth digital equipment reviews and is the 
magazine you can trust to help you decide which digital products 
to buy from cameras to scanners, printers to software. Plus 
software technique tutorials offer easy to follow creative and 
practical guidance.

Enjoy.
